"{\"uid\": \"variety.com-2024-tv-global-olympics-opening-ceremony-last-supper-dj-police-report-death-threats-1236089738\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  ByEllise Shafer  UPDATE:French DJ and activist Barbara Butch said on Monday that she has filed several police reports after receiving death threats for her participation in anOlympicsopening ceremony tableau that drew comparisons to Leonardo da Vinci's \\\"The Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8835322749426913, \"rank\": 0.130987151835502, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 62, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.0999387294147004e-12, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Prosecutor's Office confirmed toVarietythat a complaint for cyber-harassment was received and an official investigation has been launched.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999757847, \"rank\": 2.4221452180717163e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The national body in charge of combatting against online hate speech (PNLH) has appointed the central office in charge of fighting crimes against humanity and hate crimes (OCLCH) to conduct an investigation into the discriminating messages referring to the religion or sexual orientation that were addressed to her or posted online and flagged,\\\" the Prosecutor's Office said in a statement.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The facts could potentially qualify as abuse aggravated by discrimination, death threats and public incitement\\u00a0to attempt\\u00a0on\\u00a0the\\u00a0life or physical integrity of people.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Related Stories'Father Mother Sister Brother' Cinematographer Yorick Le Saux to Receive Robby M\\u00fcller AwardL.A.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinematographer\", \"score\": 0.9946990434672841, \"rank\": 0.0053292064242485716, \"text\": \"Cinematographer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinematographer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinematographer\"}, {\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorick_Le_Saux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yorick Le Saux\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorick_Le_Saux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorick_Le_Saux\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comedy 'The Dispute,' Acquired by Riley Keough and Donald Glover's Production Companies, Among Rotterdam Film Festival Projects  The scene, which featured drag queens and other members of the LGBTQ community, was the subject of backlash from the Catholic Church as well as prominent conservative figures likeRob Schneider and Candace Cameron Bure.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1129, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_K