extremely violent campaign of cyber-harassment and defamation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9344557844816662, \"rank\": 0.07014127383166745, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8835322749426913, \"rank\": 0.130987151835502, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999995681704172, \"rank\": 4.3182981689271914e-07, \"text\": \"Greek mythology\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 1679, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"score\": 0.9999999997016857, \"rank\": 2.982878893460466e-10, \"text\": \"Variety\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\"}, {\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.284028773853306e-20, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"score\": 0.9954205630967711, \"rank\": 0.0046005046165365805, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Horne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Msellati continued, \\\"She has been threatened with death, torture and rape, and has also been the target of numerous antisemitic, homophobic, sexist and grossophobic insults.\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbara Butch condemns this vile hatred directed at her, what she represents and what she stands for.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is today filing several complaints against these acts, whether committed by French nationals or foreigners, and intends to prosecute anyone who tries to intimidate her in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8835322749426913, \"rank\": 0.130987151835502, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the opening ceremony, Butch was in the center of the tableau, DJing while sporting a silver headpiece and blue dress.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an Instagram post, Butch called her look that of an \\\"Olympian music goddess.\\\"\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2514, \"end\": 2523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.284028773853306e-20, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2564, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.7826054904260481, \"rank\": 0.27221177030977445, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics organizers apologized for any misrepresentation during a press conference following the ceremony, with spokesperson Anne Descamps saying that \\\"clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group \\u2026 If people have taken any offense we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Representatives for the Paris Olympics did not immediately respond toVariety's request for comment.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Variety and iHeartRadio Podcast  The Business of Entertainment\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2982, \"end\": 2989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"score\": 0.9999999997016857, \"rank\": 2.982878893460466e-10, \"text\": \"Variety\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Variety_show\"}]}]}"